stories.title: Wise Tikolo edges thriller for Kenya
stories.subTitle: Kenya v Bermuda, 3rd ODI, Nairobi
stories.summary: Steve Tikolo drew on all his experience with a masterful 89, remaining unbeaten at the end, to take Kenya to a tense one-wicket win over Bermuda in the final one-dayer in Nairobi. In doing so, Kenya swept the series 3-0.
